{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Forge Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #9a031e;\n            --secondary-color: #d72323;\n            --accent-color: #f7cb15;\n            --background-color: #0e0e0e;\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --secondary-text-color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); opacity: 0.9; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            padding: 40px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .game-item {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n            border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .game-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(154, 3, 30, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .game-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .game-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic Elements */\n        .header-background-layer {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: repeating-linear-gradient(\n                45deg,\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 0px,\n                rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 10px,\n                transparent 10px,\n                transparent 20px\n            );\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .section-border-art {\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-right: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin: 0 -20px; /* Adjust to make borders align with parent padding */\n        }\n\n        .game-item::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: -5px;\n            left: -5px;\n            right: -5px;\n            bottom: -5px;\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n            z-index: -1;\n        }\n\n        .game-item:hover::before {\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                padding: 0 10px;\n            }\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"header-background-layer\"></div>\n        <h1>CRIMSON FORGE STUDIOS</h1>\n        <p>Crafting Worlds, Forging Legends</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-border-art\">\n                <h2>About Us</h2>\n                <p>Welcome to Crimson Forge Studios, where passion for gaming meets artistic vision. We are a dedicated team of developers, artists, and storytellers united by a singular goal: to create unforgettable gaming experiences that ignite the imagination and challenge the spirit. Our creations are born from red-hot ideas and meticulously forged into digital realities.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-border-art\">\n                <h2>Our Masterpieces</h2>\n                <div class=\"game-grid\">\n                    <div class=\"game-item\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/9a031e/ffffff?text=Game+Title+1\" alt=\"Game Title 1\">\n                        <h3>Echoes of the Crimson Moon</h3>\n                        <p>Embark on an epic fantasy adventure filled with ancient prophecies and mystical combat.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"game-item\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/d72323/ffffff?text=Game+Title+2\" alt=\"Game Title 2\">\n                        <h3>Forge & Fury</h3>\n                        <p>A fast-paced, action-packed strategy game set in a world of mechanical wonders.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"game-item\">\n                        <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/f7cb15/000000?text=Game+Title+3\" alt=\"Game Title 3\">\n                        <h3>Scarlet Horizon</h3>\n                        <p>Explore a breathtaking open world, uncover lost secrets, and shape your destiny.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <div class=\"section-border-art\">\n                <h2>Join the Forge</h2>\n                <p>Follow our journey, get exclusive updates, and be the first to know about new releases. Connect with us on:</p>\n                <p><a href=\"#\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"#\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"#\">Discord</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Forge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Website crafted with passion by the Forge Masters.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple animation for header title\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const title = document.querySelector('header h1');\n            let charIndex = 0;\n            const originalText = title.innerText;\n\n            function animateTitle() {\n                title.innerText = originalText.substring(0, charIndex) +\n                                (charIndex < originalText.length ? '|' : '');\n                charIndex++;\n                if (charIndex > originalText.length) {\n                    charIndex = 0;\n                }\n            }\n\n            setInterval(animateTitle, 200);\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}